metadata.description: CUBOTZ Port Key NFT. Super Rare and the most powerful of all CUBOTZ! Only 200 exist, with 25 reserved for airdrops and giveaways. Holders receive one free CUBOTZ NFT per main drop, early access to future drops and VIP benefits. Join our Discord and follow us on Twitter to find out how to get one!
